  "texts": [
    "The cumulative mean is 3.58.",
    "Of all the elements taken together, 59% of respondents had positive attitudes toward English language teachers.",
    "10 shows peer group opinions regarding English learning.",
    "In item no 29, only 14.8% (SA 8.8% & A 6%) said that their friends made fun of them when they spoke English.",
    "While 11.6% were neutral, 33.3% disagreed and 40.3% strongly opposed the assertion."
